- [ ] DCG summary visible on sweep session page
- [ ] All unit tests pass with comprehensive logging
- [ ] All integration tests pass

## Security Considerations

- Never auto-approve dangerous commands in sweeps
- Require explicit user approval for each exception
- Log all exception approvals with user identity
- Rate limit exception creation to prevent abuse
- Expire sweep-related exceptions after 1 hour
